(13, 'Software for CSIL Linux and CSIL Macs', '<div class="parsys main_content">\n<div class="text parbase section">\n<div class="">\n<p>Looking for Windows software? Try our <a href="CSIL-Windows-Course-Software">Windows Course Software page</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="text parbase section">\n<div class="ruled alternate">\n<p>The following is a list of Linux based software available in CSIL.</p>\n<p>If you want to get extra software installed, please contact your instructor.</p>\n<h2>Commonly used software</h2>\n<div class="table">\n<table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Name</td>\n<td>Version</td>\n<td>Availability</td>\n<td>Command</td>\n<td>Reference</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Acroread</td>\n<td>9.4.2</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/acroread</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SSH Server</td>\n<td>5.8p1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/sbin/sshd</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SSH Client</td>\n<td>5.8p1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/ssh</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>HTML to Text converter</td>\n<td>1.3.2a</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/html2text</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Mozilla Firefox</td>\n<td>6.0.1</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/firefox</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Postscript to PDF converter</td>\n<td>9.01</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/ps2pdf</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Lynx text mode browser</td>\n<td>2.8.8</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/lynx</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Elinks Text mode browser</td>\n<td>0.12</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/elinks</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>GUI text editor</td>\n<td>2.30</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/nedit</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Xemacs(graphical-based text editor)</td>\n<td>21.4</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/xemacs</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Libre Office</td>\n<td>3.3.3</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/libreoffice</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Displays directory tree</td>\n<td>2.0.0.</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/tree</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Document processor</td>\n<td>1.6.5</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/lyx</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>GNU interactive tools for a file browser</td>\n<td>1.7.4</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/git</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<h2>Development Tools</h2>\n<div class="table">\n<table width="95%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Name</td>\n<td>Version</td>\n<td>Availability</td>\n<td>Command</td>\n<td>Reference</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Awk (pattern scanning and processing language)</td>\n<td>3.1.7</td>\n<td>CSIL Linux</td>\n<td>/usr/bin/awk</td>\n<td>Ubuntu package (<a href="http://packages.ubuntu.com/">http://packages.ubuntu.com</a>